flowchart TD
  %% A new EGLE Air filing is caught and triaged — persona: N2688 Conservancy advocate
  %% The monitor spots a new Air permit filing for the landfill, classifies its risk, and alerts the advocate.
  %% (no telemetry wired yet — annotate p50/p99 here once available)
  s1["1. The daily monitor wakes at 6am<br/><small>watcher, config_loader</small>"]
  s1_ds[("config.yml (risk register + settings)")]
  s1 -. touches .-> s1_ds
  s2["2. Check EGLE nSITE for new Air filings<br/><small>watcher, nsite_client</small>"]
  s1 --> s2
  s2_ds[("EGLE nSITE Portal (Air)")]
  s2 -. touches .-> s2_ds
  s3["3. Read each new PDF and classify it against the risk register with Claude<br/><small>egle_doc_parser, risk_register</small>"]
  s2 --> s3
  s3_ds[("Anthropic Claude API")]
  s3 -. touches .-> s3_ds
  s4["4. Record the finding as a row in the case-file Sheet<br/><small>sheet_writer</small>"]
  s3 --> s4
  s4_ds[("Conservancy Case-File Sheet")]
  s4 -. touches .-> s4_ds
  s5["5. Email the advocate now if urgent, else queue for the Sunday digest<br/><small>email_alerts</small>"]
  s4 --> s5
  s5_ds[("Email Recipients (SMTP)")]
  s5 -. touches .-> s5_ds
